WEBVTT

00:01:06.039 --> 00:01:08.784
ikh bin Khatskl Lemkhen,

00:01:12.060 --> 00:01:16.816
der zibeter kind fun, in mishpokhe.

00:01:16.940 --> 00:01:19.145
mayn foter hot geheysn

00:01:19.285 --> 00:01:25.459
Avrom Yakev, oder in shtetl flegt men zogn Avrom Yankl Lemkhen,

00:01:25.459 --> 00:01:28.747
mayn muter hot geheysn Rokhe.

00:01:29.208 --> 00:01:32.274
ven un vu zayt ir geborn gevorn?

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:36.037
geborn, geborn bin ikh in shtetl

00:01:36.498 --> 00:01:40.629
oyf yidish flegt men rufn di shtetl Popelan.

00:01:40.629 --> 00:01:43.090
oyf litvish hot zi geheysn PAPILE.

00:01:44.075 --> 00:01:46.837
oyf rusish hot zi geheysn POPELYANY.

00:01:46.927 --> 00:01:49.824
der iberik iz, der yidisher Popelan.

00:01:52.276 --> 00:01:54.312
mh, ikh hob gehat

00:01:53.356 --> 00:01:54.819
velkhn yor?

00:01:55.634 --> 00:01:57.299
zayt ir geborn gevorn?

00:01:56.208 --> 00:01:59.324
geborn bin ikh in toyznt nayn hundert

00:01:59.448 --> 00:02:00.725
fertn yor.

00:02:01.591 --> 00:02:04.117
un vifl iz aykh ot itster yor?

00:02:04.380 --> 00:02:06.648
itster in dem yor bin ikh

00:02:07.666 --> 00:02:09.399
fir un nayntsik yor.

00:02:12.425 --> 00:02:15.207
mayn, mayn eltster

00:02:15.207 --> 00:02:16.182
bruder

00:02:16.897 --> 00:02:18.663
hot geheysn Yisroel.

00:02:20.997 --> 00:02:22.038
er iz

00:02:22.972 --> 00:02:23.658
als

00:02:23.765 --> 00:02:24.772
yingl

00:02:27.815 --> 00:02:33.277
 hot er zikh geshtikt in der revolutsye, un im avekgefirt, shikt UNK in Amerike.

00:02:33.451 --> 00:02:35.673
az me zol im nit arestirn.

00:02:36.033 --> 00:02:39.031
un er hot gelebt in Amerike

00:02:40.724 --> 00:02:42.980
dem grestn teyl fun zayn lebn.

00:02:45.736 --> 00:02:46.760
di

00:02:48.824 --> 00:02:52.615
di tsveyte iz geven mayn shvester Gite.

00:02:54.815 --> 00:02:55.923
zi

00:02:57.211 --> 00:03:02.507
iz in nayntsn, zi hot geendikt Shavler rusishe gimnazye

00:03:02.507 --> 00:03:03.466
Shavler

00:03:05.733 --> 00:03:06.892
gimnazye.

00:03:07.404 --> 00:03:08.455
un

00:03:08.500 --> 00:03:11.094
hot khasene gehat in draytsntn yor

00:03:11.420 --> 00:03:16.286
un avek, mit a mentsh vos iz gekumen fun dorem Afrike.

00:03:16.286 --> 00:03:18.907
un mit im avekgeforn in Afrike.

00:03:21.764 --> 00:03:24.428
di tsveyte, mayn shvester

00:03:24.447 --> 00:03:25.572
ANNA

00:03:27.502 --> 00:03:28.947
zi iz

00:03:30.202 --> 00:03:38.094
⟨gikh⟩ geendikt vi di, beyde shvester hobn geendikt Shavler gimnazye, a rusishe.

00:03:38.487 --> 00:03:42.464
un zi iz avekgeforn nokh dem oykh in Afrike.

00:03:45.727 --> 00:03:47.847
nokh dem iz gegangen

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:50.244
mayn bruder

00:03:51.059 --> 00:03:52.049
Meyer

00:03:54.957 --> 00:03:57.280
an oysnam in undzer mishpokhe

00:03:58.535 --> 00:03:59.575
vos flegt

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:02.157
 zikh

00:04:02.585 --> 00:04:04.030
mit andere

00:04:05.859 --> 00:04:07.726
yugntlekhe

00:04:08.559 --> 00:04:10.055
zikh,

00:04:11.832 --> 00:04:13.801
hargenen, zikh shlogn.

00:04:14.077 --> 00:04:16.130
er

00:04:17.047 --> 00:04:20.099
UNK oyf rusish UNK

00:04:20.849 --> 00:04:22.349
er flegt

00:04:22.349 --> 00:04:28.129
lemoshl zikh vetn mit im, er ⟨vet⟩ aribergeyn dem brik; bay undz iz dortn geven a taykh.

00:04:28.471 --> 00:04:32.178
er vet aribergeyn oyf der parentse hin un tsurik.

00:04:32.369 --> 00:04:39.890
mh er iz geven a, an ander sort, nit vi di ale iberike in Lemkhen's mishpokhe.

00:04:40.064 --> 00:04:44.514
un er hot geendikt nit, nit azoy vi ale UNK mishpokhe.

00:04:46.527 --> 00:04:47.900
nokh dem iz geven

00:04:47.945 --> 00:04:50.116
a bruder, Sholem.

00:04:52.923 --> 00:04:53.980
vos iz

00:04:54.408 --> 00:04:56.562
mit undz iz geven di gantse tsayt.

00:04:57.445 --> 00:04:58.334
un

00:04:58.779 --> 00:04:59.915
nokh dem

00:04:59.915 --> 00:05:01.642
bin ikh geven, Khatskl.

00:05:03.149 --> 00:05:05.304
geboyrn in f- fertn yor.

00:05:08.650 --> 00:05:12.327
vu hot ir gelebt? vi hot oysgezen di shtetl?

00:05:12.327 --> 00:05:15.074
di, di shtub vu ir hot gelebt?

00:05:13.274 --> 00:05:16.672
mir, m- mir hobn ge-

00:05:16.700 --> 00:05:18.280
ikh hob gelebt

00:05:18.556 --> 00:05:20.255
mit der mishpokhe

00:05:20.497 --> 00:05:22.634
in PAPILE, in Popelan.

00:05:24.462 --> 00:05:25.705
vayle

00:05:25.964 --> 00:05:29.165
⟨kh'hob⟩ mayn foter iz fun Zhager, ZAGARE.

00:05:30.385 --> 00:05:32.405
ober er hot khasene gehat

00:05:32.815 --> 00:05:33.620
far

00:05:34.824 --> 00:05:35.982
Rokhe

00:05:36.275 --> 00:05:37.164
Zaks

00:05:38.941 --> 00:05:39.897
un

00:05:40.139 --> 00:05:43.629
Zaks iz geven a groyser unternemer in

00:05:43.629 --> 00:05:45.415
in yene bagrifn.

00:05:45.927 --> 00:05:47.238
in yene tsaytn.

00:05:47.649 --> 00:05:48.588
un

00:05:51.564 --> 00:05:52.621
der

00:05:53.082 --> 00:05:54.984
ir foter hot gehat

00:05:55.310 --> 00:05:57.855
a groyse shtub mit, mit

00:05:57.855 --> 00:05:59.439
mit a sakh tsimer

00:05:59.697 --> 00:06:03.558
iz er aribergeforn dort un gelozn in Zhager

00:06:03.558 --> 00:06:07.488
zayn shvester vos hot khasene gehat mit a mentshn fun Kurland.

00:06:09.805 --> 00:06:14.474
ikh muz dos dermonen vayle nokh dem zaynen mir ariber in Zhager.

00:06:15.880 --> 00:06:16.769
mh

00:06:17.978 --> 00:06:22.895
mir zaynen geven in Papile biz zikh ongehoybn

00:06:24.115 --> 00:06:26.202
di ershte velt milkhome.

00:06:28.317 --> 00:06:29.122
az

00:06:29.735 --> 00:06:30.303
m

00:06:30.798 --> 00:06:34.404
di daytshn militer iz shoyn geven noent tsum shtetl

00:06:35.793 --> 00:06:38.743
hot mayn foter vos hot gehandlt mit holts

00:06:38.780 --> 00:06:41.435
un gehat a ferd mit a vogn

00:06:41.435 --> 00:06:43.533
hot gezogt "me muz forn in Zhager."

00:06:43.960 --> 00:06:44.844
do

00:06:44.844 --> 00:06:45.862
do

00:06:46.559 --> 00:06:49.929
trefn zikh zi beyde armeyen, di rusishe mit

00:06:51.115 --> 00:06:55.717
zaynen mir geforn, hot er ayngeshpant a ferd, un mir hobn zikh avekgezetst.

00:06:57.292 --> 00:06:59.328
foter un muter, ikh un

00:06:59.452 --> 00:07:00.408
Sholem.

00:07:04.666 --> 00:07:07.681
un mir zaynen geforn in Zhager.

00:07:08.294 --> 00:07:11.090
hot zikh aroysgevizn az

00:07:12.682 --> 00:07:13.587
der

00:07:14.622 --> 00:07:17.117
hoypt komandir fun rusisher armey

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:18.886
Nikolay Nikolayevitsh

00:07:19.179 --> 00:07:20.219
der

00:07:21.609 --> 00:07:25.045
der onkl fun ts- fun tsar, fun

00:07:26.452 --> 00:07:27.492
hot

00:07:28.055 --> 00:07:30.817
geheysn fun Kovner Gubernye

00:07:31.329 --> 00:07:36.267
bazaytikn ale yidn vayle zey kenen reydn oyf yidish azoy vi daytsh.

00:07:37.505 --> 00:07:39.372
hot men alemen aroysgetribn.

00:07:39.665 --> 00:07:41.634
az mir zaynen gekumen in

00:07:41.791 --> 00:07:42.849
Zhager

00:07:43.698 --> 00:07:45.262
iz gev- zaynen shoyn

00:07:45.622 --> 00:07:49.019
ale geven aroys, ⟨zaynen⟩ geven nor tsvey

00:07:49.019 --> 00:07:50.242
yidn geblibn

00:07:50.245 --> 00:07:55.150
hobn gekrogn fun ISPRAVNIK hobn ⟨zey⟩ gekrogn a derloybenish oyf nokh a tog tsu zayn.

00:07:55.392 --> 00:07:56.993
dos iz geven der dokter

00:07:57.029 --> 00:07:58.002
un der

00:07:58.632 --> 00:08:01.051
balebos fun grestn

00:08:01.051 --> 00:08:02.845
magazin in Zhager.

00:08:03.256 --> 00:08:05.714
ober in Zhager hot men nit gekent blaybn.

00:08:06.310 --> 00:08:07.857
zaynen geforn vayter

00:08:09.162 --> 00:08:11.941
un mir zaynen gekumen tsum breg fun

00:08:13.769 --> 00:08:15.333
fun a taykh.

00:08:17.330 --> 00:08:18.995
iz gekumen fun

00:08:19.321 --> 00:08:21.543
a groysn teyl fun Lite.

00:08:21.869 --> 00:08:23.365
gants Zamet.

00:08:25.514 --> 00:08:27.055
Kovner hobn gekent

00:08:27.100 --> 00:08:31.314
vayle der bafel iz geven az yidn muzn farlozn Kovner Gubernye.

00:08:32.045 --> 00:08:36.460
iz Kovner hobn gekent, ver es hot gehat a meglekhkeyt iz avekgeforn

00:08:36.804 --> 00:08:37.810
in Vilne.

00:08:38.035 --> 00:08:39.734
oykh nit Kovner Gubernye.

00:08:40.314 --> 00:08:44.493
ober azoy iz nit geven veynik vos hobn gekent forn in Vilne.

00:08:45.410 --> 00:08:47.761
hot zikh tsuzamengeklibn oyfn

00:08:47.789 --> 00:08:49.606
breg fun a taykh

00:08:49.848 --> 00:08:54.820
vos dan hot zi geheysn mit a daytshn nomen ⟨AA⟩.

00:08:56.446 --> 00:08:59.495
dos iz mistome a toykh, a taykh DAUGAVA.

00:09:00.597 --> 00:09:04.625
hot zikh tsuzamengeklibn der ershter tog suke-, shvues

00:09:04.951 --> 00:09:06.430
zaynen geven ale

00:09:07.044 --> 00:09:10.244
oyfn breg un gevart oyf barzhes vos zol firn in

00:09:10.621 --> 00:09:11.527
Rige.

00:09:14.334 --> 00:09:16.077
zaynen gekumen barzhes

00:09:16.105 --> 00:09:17.360
un dortn oyfn

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:18.204
plats

00:09:18.215 --> 00:09:20.403
s'iz geven der ershter tog shvues

00:09:20.797 --> 00:09:22.377
hot nokh a khazn

00:09:23.328 --> 00:09:24.622
gedavnt

00:09:25.640 --> 00:09:26.410
un nokh

00:09:27.260 --> 00:09:33.515
un hoykh oyfn kol gezogt ATO BEKHARTONU MIKOL HOAMIM, du host undz oysgeklibn fun ale felker.

00:09:35.900 --> 00:09:40.096
dos blaybt in, in zikorn, azoyne, eyntslheyt.

00:09:41.604 --> 00:09:44.908
nu, ⟨hob ikh tsugegangen⟩ mayn tante

00:09:44.928 --> 00:09:49.852
hot moyre gehat zikh tsu zitsn oyf di barzhes az me tut dertrinken.

00:09:49.852 --> 00:09:54.845
ober m'hot undz avekgefirt in Rige, un a yidisher komitet hot alemen ayngeordnt.

00:09:56.200 --> 00:09:59.047
dort in Rige zenen mir geven zeyer a kurtse tsayt

00:09:59.997 --> 00:10:01.308
un mir

00:10:01.617 --> 00:10:07.332
mit, fun Rige, di aroysgetribene, ⟨oder⟩ geheysn hobn mir

00:10:07.895 --> 00:10:11.436
antlofene, PABEGELIAI, BEZHENTSY.

00:10:11.436 --> 00:10:12.260
BEZHENTSY.

00:10:13.852 --> 00:10:17.103
iz di BEZHENTSes hot men geheysn forn vayter.

00:10:17.463 --> 00:10:19.550
az in Rige zoln zey nit blaybn.

00:10:20.568 --> 00:10:24.460
mayn foter hot oysgeklibn dem noentstn ort vos me hot forgeleygt.

00:10:24.837 --> 00:10:27.954
Mogilov, vos dos iz nokh ⟨oykh⟩ Vaysrusland.

00:10:29.124 --> 00:10:30.215
in Mogilov

00:10:31.216 --> 00:10:34.501
zaynen mir geven efsher tsvey khadoshim.

00:10:35.992 --> 00:10:39.952
un di Mogilover yidn hobn geha- gehaltn az BEZHENTSes, dos iz

00:10:40.531 --> 00:10:41.892
knape mentshn.

00:10:43.687 --> 00:10:46.803
ober zikh ibergehoybn in Mogilov

00:10:48.142 --> 00:10:51.514
STAVKA VERKHOVNOGO, der GLAVNOKOMANDYUSHCHEGO

00:10:51.514 --> 00:10:54.160
hot men gezogt az BEZHNETSes muzn aroys.

00:10:54.419 --> 00:10:57.927
un m'hot forgeleygt finf shtet vu tsu forn.

00:10:57.927 --> 00:11:00.050
mayn foter hot oysgeklibn

00:11:00.190 --> 00:11:05.079
dem, di noenste shtot, oykh shoyn in mitn Rusland, in PENZA.

00:11:05.388 --> 00:11:07.222
zaynen mir geven in PENZA.

00:11:08.645 --> 00:11:10.900
finf yor zaynen mir opgeven in PENZA.

00:11:11.514 --> 00:11:14.042
UNK vi mir hobn oyfn breg

00:11:14.042 --> 00:11:17.582
fun taykh, mir hobn getrofn di tante mit ir man

00:11:17.582 --> 00:11:20.902
vos er iz geven a spetsyalist in farbn

00:11:20.902 --> 00:11:22.732
farbn shtof

00:11:24.001 --> 00:11:28.706
un dorfishe flegn nokh dan zeyer fil aleyn vebn, un es

00:11:28.726 --> 00:11:30.613
un flegn brengen

00:11:30.650 --> 00:11:31.741
tsu farbn.

00:11:32.185 --> 00:11:34.205
az mir zaynen gekumen in PENZA

00:11:35.459 --> 00:11:39.993
hobn mir nit vayt gefunen a ort vu me hot avekgeshtelt a groysn kesl

00:11:40.235 --> 00:11:41.050
un

00:11:41.050 --> 00:11:43.064
mir zaynen gevorn farbers.

00:11:45.314 --> 00:11:47.755
ikh, natirlekh, bin avek lernen.

00:11:48.723 --> 00:11:53.004
in a y- folkshul, fun UNK a yidisher a kurtse tsayt.

00:11:53.380 --> 00:11:56.159
nokh dem ⟨hob ikh⟩ gelernt in gimnazye

00:11:56.890 --> 00:11:58.640
fun brider Khaykin

00:11:59.152 --> 00:12:02.234
a yidish- a yidishe gimnazye oyf rusish

00:12:02.324 --> 00:12:04.462
vos ⟨iz⟩ evakuirt fun Minsk.

00:12:05.395 --> 00:12:07.533
tsvey klasn hobn mir ge-

00:12:09.665 --> 00:12:10.722
gelernt

00:12:12.145 --> 00:12:14.097
in der gimnazye.

00:12:15.824 --> 00:12:16.780
un

00:12:16.972 --> 00:12:19.649
do iz forgekumen di revolutsye.

00:12:22.608 --> 00:12:23.598
iz

00:12:24.768 --> 00:12:26.905
di komunistishe partey

00:12:27.535 --> 00:12:30.820
hot derklert az ale gimnazyes darf men farmakhn

00:12:31.484 --> 00:12:32.845
az dos iz

00:12:33.509 --> 00:12:34.870
zey greytn nor

00:12:35.180 --> 00:12:37.452
kadren far der burzhuazye

00:12:39.230 --> 00:12:40.473
un mir zaynen ge-

00:12:41.626 --> 00:12:43.342
mir zaynen avek nokh

00:12:44.124 --> 00:12:48.373
f- az Khaykin's gimn- gimnazye, di yi- di yidishe oyf rusish

00:12:48.373 --> 00:12:50.581
hot zikh farmakht, zaynen mir nokh geven

00:12:50.789 --> 00:12:52.758
in a rusisher gimnazye

00:12:53.844 --> 00:12:54.817
ober az m-

00:12:55.025 --> 00:12:57.348
mayn klas, der driter klas

00:12:57.573 --> 00:13:00.841
iz gezesn di yidn, bay, hobn gehat a bazundere rey

00:13:02.484 --> 00:13:07.813
un di rusishe, s'iz geven tsvishn di rusishe azoyne vos flegn undz tshepenen

00:13:07.816 --> 00:13:09.245
vos flegn shlogn.

00:13:09.892 --> 00:13:12.080
hobn mir zikh baklogt mit dem direktor

00:13:13.334 --> 00:13:16.799
i der, der, un dem klasn dertsier.

00:13:16.844 --> 00:13:19.471
iz gekumen der direktor, hot gezogt az

00:13:19.882 --> 00:13:22.154
er vet zey a- bazaytikn

00:13:22.750 --> 00:13:25.127
in a gimnazye vos hot gelernt

00:13:25.127 --> 00:13:26.559
Lermontov mit

00:13:27.070 --> 00:13:29.343
mit Kh- UNK

00:13:29.838 --> 00:13:31.168
s'iz geven groyse

00:13:31.171 --> 00:13:33.931
zol men bafaln yidn?

00:13:33.931 --> 00:13:36.751
zey zaynen punkt azoyne balebatim vi ⟨ir⟩.

00:13:37.533 --> 00:13:38.270
un

00:13:38.545 --> 00:13:39.924
er un

00:13:40.267 --> 00:13:41.881
a inspektor iz geven

00:13:42.309 --> 00:13:44.744
hobn gemakht a groysn tuml, un s-

00:13:44.744 --> 00:13:47.284
m'hot oyfgehert tsu bafaln undz.

00:13:47.284 --> 00:13:49.711
vayle mir hobn gehat a bazundere rey.

00:13:53.564 --> 00:13:56.005
nor az s'iz geven di revolutsye

00:13:58.340 --> 00:14:00.717
hobn di bolshevikes bashlosn az

00:14:00.717 --> 00:14:02.705
me darf farmakhn ale gimnazyes

00:14:04.364 --> 00:14:05.810
un efenen

00:14:08.195 --> 00:14:09.168
klubn.

00:14:10.220 --> 00:14:13.471
der tsenter klub iz geven a yidisher.

00:14:14.405 --> 00:14:17.538
dortn iz geven tsvey forzitsers

00:14:18.556 --> 00:14:19.411
a

00:14:19.585 --> 00:14:20.469
eyn

00:14:20.480 --> 00:14:22.182
yor, eyn halb yor

00:14:22.182 --> 00:14:23.630
eyner un eyner.

00:14:23.855 --> 00:14:26.634
eyner fun di forzitser iz geven Lemkhen.

00:14:26.808 --> 00:14:30.565
ikh hob nokh a bild vu ikh zits als forzitser.

00:14:34.250 --> 00:14:39.942
dortn iz geven alts litvishe kinder, ale fun Lite

00:14:39.970 --> 00:14:41.770
inem, in tsentn klub.

00:14:41.995 --> 00:14:45.112
litvishe tsi fun Lite?

00:14:44.400 --> 00:14:45.590
fun Lite, fun Lite

00:14:45.590 --> 00:14:47.180
nor yidishe mistome.

00:14:46.247 --> 00:14:47.427
yidishe.

00:14:47.427 --> 00:14:48.747
a yidisher, der

00:14:48.747 --> 00:14:52.777
tsenter klub iz geven a yidisher, ober zaynen ale geven faktish

00:14:52.777 --> 00:14:54.730
nor fun Lite.

00:14:56.829 --> 00:14:58.173
nu?

00:15:00.541 --> 00:15:01.484
ober

00:15:01.484 --> 00:15:04.180
az s'iz, az s'iz geven di revolutsye

00:15:05.114 --> 00:15:08.399
un mir zaynen geblibn in a klub

00:15:08.793 --> 00:15:11.690
tsugezogt hot men az m'hot tsi eyne

